<!-- hero section -->
<section class="hero is-medium is-warning hero-background-image">
    <div class="hero-cta">
        <h2 class="heading-title">Protect our earth</h2>
        <p>
        Nature- A Boon for All. Nature is the mother of all, as it helps to sustain our life. It is our companion since eternity.Our lives as human beings started on this planet Earth and since then we are exhausting its resources. We are giving challenges to nature by doing activities as hunting down animals, cutting down trees, releasing poisonous gases and polluting rivers. Greenhive app is here to spread the message around so that every person can become a responsible global citizen who can contribute to saving our planet.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<!--main-section-->
<section id="Aboutus" class="intro">
    <div class="flex-row">
        <h2 class="title heading-title">About Us</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-row">
        <p>
        We are all nature lovers and have interests in wildlife and environment protection. We would like to know about species that are endangered  and the general status of the Earth. Also make getting involved with a community surrounding that idea more easier and convenient. Greenhive is a Conservation app where people can join communities related to different resources. All users can post about nature conservation and environment protection.

        </p>
    </div>
</section>

